===== 黃俊英「走路工」賄選案 =====
陳菊競選總部在12月8日晚間舉發，黃俊英陣營有人發放「走路工」，涉嫌賄選，並公布側錄影像，此震撼彈衝擊了黃俊英的選情。

「走路工事件」最後法院判決此賄選案，被告綽號「古意」古鋅酩幫忙動員，與綽號「黑松」蔡能祥一同發放賄款，分別判處有期徒刑3年6個月、有期徒刑9個月定讞<ref>{{cite news |language =zh-tw | url =http://www.nownews.com/2009/10/21/138-2522859.htm | title =高雄走路工案　「黑松」蔡能祥上吊身亡 | publisher =[[今日新聞|今日新聞]] | date =2009-10-21 | accessdate =2009-10-21}}</ref>。在經歷兩次高雄市市長敗選之後，黃俊英表示尊重司法判決，將擔任政治志工，全力輔選黨內立委及總統候選人贏得勝選<ref>{{cite news| language =zh-tw| url =http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2007/new/nov/18/today-fo7-2.htm| title =黃俊英：尊重判決 當政治志工| publisher =[[自由時報|自由時報]]| date =2007-11-16| accessdate =2007-11-16| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20071121022208/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2007/new/nov/18/today-fo7-2.htm| archivedate =2007-11-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language =zh-tw | url =http://epochweekly.com/b5/048/3983.htm | title =高雄市長選舉官司陳菊勝出 國民黨反而暗自高興 | publisher =[[新紀元周刊|新紀元周刊]] | date =2007-11-16 | accessdate =2007-11-16 | archive-date =2010-11-10 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20101110171343/http://www.epochweekly.com/b5/048/3983.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

檢方也有查出幕後指使者為「[[黃俊英|黃俊英]]競選總部[[雲林縣|雲林縣]]後援會」[[執行長|執行長]][[蘇萬基|蘇萬基]]、「[[資源回收|資源回收]]商」[[總經理|總經理]][[楊慶德|楊慶德]]，隨即對兩人開出拘票，楊慶德得知事情曝光搭機逃往香港，蘇萬基則是在律師陪同投案訊後飭回，但限制其住居<ref>{{cite news | language =zh-tw | url =http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1002/6/9/5/100269554.html?coluid=69&kindid=1813&docid=100269554&mdate=0911123624 | title =涉指使　花錢動員走路工案拘提楊慶德蘇萬基 | publisher =[[中國評論通訊社|中國評論通訊社]] | date =2006-12-15 | accessdate =2006-12-15 | archive-date =2015-09-23 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150923203016/http://www.chinareviewnews.com/doc/1002/6/9/5/100269554.html?coluid=69&kindid=1813&docid=100269554&mdate=0911123624 | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language =zh-tw | url =http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/15/n1558495.htm | title =疑高雄走路工案藏鏡人 蘇萬基投案訊後飭回 | publisher =[[大紀元|大紀元]] | date =2006-12-18 | accessdate =2006-12-18 | archive-date =2014-01-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140112062538/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/15/n1558495.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language =zh-tw | url =http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/15/n1557660.htm | title =走路工案 疑蘇萬基主導 | publisher =[[大紀元|大紀元]] | date =2006-12-15 | accessdate =2006-12-15 | archive-date =2014-01-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140112064221/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/15/n1557660.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| language =zh-tw| url =http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2006/new/dec/16/today-p1.htm| title =蘇萬基 支持黃俊英 幫忙動員| publisher =[[自由時報|自由時報]]| date =2006-12-18| accessdate =2006-12-18| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20070108211154/http://www.libertytimes.com.tw/2006/new/dec/16/today-p1.htm| archivedate =2007-01-08}}</ref>。後來經檢警透過家屬聯繫，楊慶德入境高雄時遭逮捕移送，並坦承兩度出資找「古意」動員，只是不察「菊營青年軍」發給千元，通聯紀錄也未查出與菊營有關，破除了藍營「陰謀論」的說法<ref>{{cite news | language =zh-tw | url =http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/18/n1561074.htm | title =走路工案 楊慶德到案坦承出資託人動員 | publisher =[[大紀元|大紀元]] | date =2006-12-18 | accessdate =2006-12-18 | archive-date =2014-01-12 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140112063510/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/18/n1561074.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | language =zh-tw | url =http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/19/n1561302.htm | title =楊慶德返台坦承 兩度找古動員 | publisher =[[大紀元|大紀元]] | date =2006-12-19 | accessdate =2006-12-19 | archive-date =2009-06-23 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20090623142756/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/6/12/19/n1561302.htm | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

